---
title: Middle Eastern Double Honey Pork & Garlic Rice with Mint Yoghurt & Cucumber Salad
description: Our warming Middle Eastern spice does an amazing job of coating tender double pork strips, making this meal a real standout. Along with flavourful garlic rice, cucumber salsa and a mint yoghurt drizzle, it’s sure to become a household hit!
